<h3><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Disclosure of trading in own shares</span></strong></h3>
<p>March 16, 2020: <a href="/sites/sgcom.master/files/rachats_actions_reporting_16mars2020_en_.pdf" target="_blank" class="blockLink">Disclosure of trading in own shares from March 9 to March 12, 2020 - PDF</a></p>
