<p>June 26, 2019: <a href="/sites/sgcom.master/files/rachats_actions_reporting_25juin2019_en-.pdf" target="_blank" class="blockLink">Disclosure of trading in own shares from June 17 to June 24, 2019 - PDF</a></p>
<p>May 24, 2019: <a href="/sites/sgcom.master/files/rachats_actions_reporting_24mai2019_en-.pdf" target="_blank" class="blockLink">Disclosure of trading in own shares from May 16 to May 22, 2019 - PDF</a></p>
<p>May 17, 2019: <a href="/sites/sgcom.master/files/rachats_actions_reporting_17mai2019_en-.pdf" target="_blank" class="blockLink">Disclosure of trading in own shares from May 10 to May 15, 2019 - PDF</a></p>
<p>March 8, 2019: <a href="/sites/sgcom.master/files/rachats_actions_reporting_8mars2019_en-.pdf" target="_blank" class="blockLink">Disclosure of trading in own shares from Feb. 27 to March 5, 2019 - PDF</a></p>
